{"tid":1474023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何謂資訊戰？台灣網站超強懶人包！","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:00:56.000Z","uid":138409,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6d77247fcfd5ca5e75d16112c5ba135e099fcbd7","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://watchout.tw/projects/info-warfare/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwatchout.tw%2Fprojects%2Finfo-warfare%2F&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdr2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=5eb2699c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://watchout.tw/projects/info-warfare/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家多少都聽過貿易戰、金融戰、外交戰等等，資訊戰就是各種「戰」的其中一種。可怕的是，資訊戰會與其他的「戰」搭配，例如在斷你邦交國之前，用輿論攻擊放假消息，讓你以為政府維持邦交國是在浪費錢。像這樣，多種手段搭配軍事威脅，就是戰爭的現代型態：無煙硝的「混合戰」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">資訊戰，目的是「瓦解民主社會的互信機制」，讓原本對立的人更對立，讓原本不願意溝通的人變得更難溝通，更厭惡彼此。</span>然而，只是傳一些假消息，人們並不會輕易上當。有效的資訊戰，必須先建立信任、消除戒心，再投其所好。攻擊者會發佈你喜歡的訊息，加上些微改造，內容可能是七分真、三分假，慢慢讓你的認知、判斷、行為變得更容易被操弄。此時，任何其他混合戰的手段，都會變得更容易發動，更有效果。<br />\n<br />\n台灣原本就有很多對立，如果我們持續讓敵人見縫插針，我們的民主社會只會更分裂，更脆弱。我們要能看清誰是敵對勢力代理人，加強個人防禦能力及集體合作，才能共同守護台灣。在認識資訊戰之後，我們也要問：然後呢？能做些什麼？"},{"pid":"47b77685399f7b10b8ed920d79d4b2bd721c0fb9","tid":1474023,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c1b1f728155421eb2eb6c747cb6e5c0644da31","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96f2428fe233179be272097758ace71b4bb98320","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ffa8864b6b6f517aa585323dadf275f6b5e12b6","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc4d60519bf4184bb9d07eb436df5f3bb14d9b45","tid":1474023,"uid":106851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caa9b9fa45732fa8255030789aa8de82a2dcb8e3","tid":1474023,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>8月15日</strong>：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"80f32e31f6e95806cf6843e8636262f7e27303f2","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"有關香港方面嘅資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n反「反送中」<br />\n2019/8/11，香港「反送中」全境抗爭運動第十個週末，一位女性民眾（後證實為救護員）右眼被香港警察「布袋彈」擊中，眼球爆裂、頭骨碎裂。中國官方媒體《央視》於官方網站、微博稱該名女子是「被同伙擊中眼睛」、示威者「是領錢參加遊行」。（<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20190813-morning-brief/）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20190813-morning-brief%2F%EF%BC%89&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdr2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=4972779e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20190813-morning-brief/）</a><br />\n<br />\n8/12，中國港澳辦公室召開記者會，稱示威者是「嚴重暴力犯罪」，「已出現恐怖主義的苗頭」。（<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49316195）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49316195%EF%BC%89&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdr2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=8065e67f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49316195%EF%BC%89&h=3ec702c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49316195）</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">《紐約時報》報導指出，中国利用國營、社交媒體散播愛國及反西方情緒，扭曲照片和影片的脈絡，將「反送中」大規模民主抗爭運動塑造為「極少數激進暴力份子，不受香港民意支持、被外國勢力教唆，企圖分裂中国」的「恐怖主義」活動。</span>（<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/13/world/asia/hong-kong-protests-china.html）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-china.html%EF%BC%89&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdr2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=588390ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/13/world/asia/hong-kong-protests-china.html）</a>"},{"pid":"093ed2e62f0869984251636cb5ee38847381d2c6","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e8ed57017a193803133adae897448e95572b44d2","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fbcaf89e2201fdb709adcb98ce33d970f4c57e88","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a95ea451b6f0da95fb6a1685eff1f442124ccd1b","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"919fdf9c8a7fb699a49a8b3f4e86339a1f7207d8","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"cc115116d2ebf3bf120fea00d6b8853e6665c913","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"bump"},{"pid":"7852b361d9cb8900f9851677c807f3a83f9a0dae","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1e82743a75028b5fa4b964aed4d5a98df3120a72","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bec085d2785bc47c2199a8a6b13d8f2efe08a374","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:54:35.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1ec4e40a1c6e83189fffa46ea54b35b17f5c862f","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"495260ec59013c341f28e3ba1acf3e8612be393e","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"24068d5ee59682f78db9d3a9d9c58a9f5fbcff0d","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"cb42c3ab6bbfca95b07b4fd65dbc505b8a512bf1","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:55:23.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"68dc576406f4287a9f7148e9f7f9c18dcda6fdfe","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"bd80c30cf8fde40670f4a23001126c96558251a3","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d9e943017b87ecd32b05271c36bfdf7bbb31e18e","tid":1474023,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"8db22375c06fecbff9597b1acad0fce248749664","tid":1474023,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:56:50.000Z","msg":"藍絲分化都唔做<br />\n資訊戰喎 嘥氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無撚得救 成日話分化班藍絲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472943</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}